{Get & Post Request}

(Get)

> Used to GET some response
> Data sent in Query string (limited, string data & visible in URL)


(Post)

> Used to POST something (for Create/ Write ? Update)
> Datat sent via request body (any type of data)

{Handling Post request}

> Set up POST request route to get some response.
> Pares POST request data.

[app.use(express.urlenccoded({extended: true}))]
[app.use(express.json()); ]